T1  - An Optimum Geographical Distribution of Publicity Expenditure in a Private Organisation
AU  - Zentler, A. P.
AU  - Ryde, Dorothy
Y1  - 1956/07/01
PY  - 1956
DA  - 1956/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2.4.337
